Within the reception studies, this article is about the viewers of the situation comedy Friends in Spain. Taking into account a situation comedy, pleasure is regarded as a light viewing to laugh and forget about the problems. First of all, I will look into consume of this TV show. Why does the Spanish audience want to watch this comedy? Which kind of gratification do they get? Secondly, Spanish viewer’s attitude towards this “American universe” will be described. This research uses a combination of quantitative and qualitative methods to study the distinctive viewing of the Spanish fans of this TV sitcom. In the first phase, existing data comes from 2.494 online questionnaires. This analysis provides a context for the qualitative data that is based on two focus groups and ten in-depth interviews.